### Presign for CV upload (no auth required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "cv",
  "contentType": "application/pdf",
  "extension": "pdf"
}

###

### Presign for content image (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "purpose": "content-image",
  "contentType": "image/webp",
  "extension": "webp"
}

###

### No auth for non-cv purpose (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "content-image",
  "contentType": "image/webp",
  "extension": "webp"
}

###

### Guide token for admin-only purpose (expect 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{guideToken}}

{
  "purpose": "badge-image",
  "contentType": "image/webp",
  "extension": "webp"
}

###

### Invalid purpose value (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/uploads/presign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "invalid-purpose",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg",
  "extension": "jpg"
}
